The patches in this directory (except 018-bundled-zlib-mingw-cflags.patch, which
is original to this project) are taken from the MSYS2 `mingw-w64-v8` package in
the msys2/MINGW-packages repository:

    https://github.com/msys2/MINGW-packages/tree/master/mingw-w64-v8

They are redistributed here under that repository's license, reproduced verbatim
below. See README.md in this directory for provenance and local modifications.

Note that the patches are diffs against V8 and Abseil source; the resulting
patched code remains subject to its own upstream licenses (BSD-3-Clause and
Apache-2.0 respectively). See ../../THIRD_PARTY_LICENSES.md.

